Resource
Purpose
🔐 KMS Key
Encrypts S3 bucket, DynamoDB, Kendra, and CloudWatch logs.
🧠 Amazon Kendra Index
Provides semantic search on S3 documents.
📁 S3 Bucket (cloudops-ai-knowledge)
Stores your troubleshooting documents.
🦾 AWS Lambda Function (CloudOpsAI)
Main logic to process queries, retrieve context using Kendra, and get AI response via Bedrock (Claude v2).
💬 Amazon Lex Bot (CloudOpsAssistantBot)
Chatbot interface where users can ask questions.
🧭 Lex Bot Alias (TestAlias)
Deployable version of the Lex bot used for testing or connecting with web UI.
🧾 IAM Roles
For Lambda, Lex, and Kendra to access each other and AWS services securely.
🗂️ DynamoDB Table (CloudOpsChatHistory)
Stores chat history (future use, not yet active in Lambda).
📜 CloudWatch Log Group
Captures logs from Lambda for monitoring/troubleshooting.
